          <li>Improve network availability handling</li>
          <li>Fix issues with fetching e-mail when Mail is not autostarted</li>
          <li>Notify the user when a calendar event is included in a message</li>
          <li>Improve performance when switching between folders</li>
          <li>Updated translations</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
